    "title": "Now Hiring Store Manager at Khadim's",
    "description": "Grow your career with Khadim's! We are hiring a Store Manager for our Dhanbad team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Khadim's:\nKhadim's is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Prepare daily sales reports and share insights with management\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n• Manage shrinkage and reduce stock discrepancies\n• Implement promotional activities and in-store campaigns\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in KPI Management\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Team Leadership\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Dhanbad, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Khadim's!",
